{"tid":319400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教 歷 史 ， 講 真 相 （陶傑）","createTime":"2017-07-12T18:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T02:16:01.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7554877a9d62d20ff8fb57dec3e11342dfc69ddf","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:03:01.000Z","msg":"【即時文摘】教歷史，講真相（陶傑）<br />\n<br />\n中學恢復中國歷史科，特區的中學教師，教不教得來？<br />\n<br />\n教不來。<span style=\"color: red;\">因為中國歷史的教科書有許多矛盾和謊言，其中一些，被中國的歷史學者自己踢爆，如「太平天國」之亂──國民黨的羅爾綱，共產黨的范文瀾和無數給「改造思想」的學者，都說是「革命」和「起義」，但近年許多大陸學者指出：什麼革命起義，不過是一個邪教。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果洪秀全是革命英雄，屠殺太平匪亂的曾國藩，應該是大漢奸、大戰犯，但曾國藩卻獲得尊崇。二十一世紀網絡世代，香港的年輕人不聽中國父母的信口雌黃，自打嘴巴的連篇謊言，會在網絡尋找真相。<br />\n<br />\n中國歷史科一旦「恢復」，可以保證：以後中國歷史教師在課室，講到所謂「鴉片戰爭」之後，教師在台上講一句，台下就有學生駁十句。<br />\n<br />\n中國歷史教科書的「偽歷史」（Fake History）真是講不完。例如日俄戰爭，中國歷史教科書蓄意隱瞞真相。<br />\n<br />\n一九○○年，俄國趁清國爆發拳亂，俄國以「保護東清鐵路」為由，出兵佔奪滿洲即中國東北三省，長達五年。<br />\n<br />\n俄國侵滿，對日本構成威脅。日本向清國徵得同意，出兵東北，並得到大清國的支援，共同抗俄。日軍是主力，戰勝俄國，收回九成多的土地，歸還清國。<br />\n<br />\n當然，日本不是做善事的。日本嚴正要求：鑑於保護滿洲，日軍陣亡十萬，清國割讓旅順大連，南滿鐵路經營權以及沿線的森林礦產，並允許日本在鐵路兩邊駐軍。此所謂「會議東三省事宜正約」。從此日本駐軍，並與張作霖父子等軍閥共治。<br />\n<br />\n這就是日本的「一帶一路」之始，然後開始向東北殖民。此一內容，與今日中國的「一帶一路」性質雷同，只不過後來清室覆亡，民國成立，然後蔣中正北伐，中國的民族主義高漲，不承認「會議東三省事宜正約」。在強行收回漢口租界之後，又想收回東北。<br />\n<br />\n日本則指中國不守信用。當然，蔣中正時代的中國，認為「會議東三省事宜正約」是歷史文件，已無現實意義，但日本認為，承諾是要遵守的。<br />\n<br />\n今日中國的「一帶一路」，賄賂第三世界政府，簽下許多佔人便宜的不平等條約，等人家改朝換代，一樣會大打出手。這就是「以古鑑今」的意義。但是，一來歷史的真實版本，教師懂嗎？二來歷史的意義，以日滿中的思想，引證「一帶一路」，歷史教師敢討論嗎？不敢的。教歷史，這個大題目，特府是無力承受的。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170712/56941295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170712%2F56941295&d=tn6kEAKrQafbM6FcrJe3SUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0b8ddddf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170712%2F56941295&h=849d530a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170712/56941295</a>"},{"pid":"54652737ed1c3303e5b355b7a36e0460dfbe5e38","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"孫中山領導推翻滿清 建立民國"},{"pid":"e7c0e1540fd45d4b0b983a98e0b1f45f72a96b54","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"中國歷史有幾多係真實客觀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea51607848349927a8326049a8f147a33deff171","tid":319400,"uid":125752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:12:47.000Z","msg":"讀壞腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb2435f40ad48184ce65d2f61170ffd5248deeb","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"教不來。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為中國歷史的教科書有許多矛盾和謊</span></span>言，其中一些，被中國的歷史學者自己踢爆，如「太平天國」之亂──國民黨的羅爾綱，共產黨的范文瀾和無數給「改造思想」的學者，都說是「革命」和「起義」，但近年許多大陸學者指出：什麼革命起義，不過是一個邪教。<br />\n<br />\n有些人睇咗電視劇或小說<br />\n就以為係真歷史<br />\n<br />\n宋朝就有人罵人係&quot;漢奸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cef4d34af35aa7b16353817580a60a1f4328b6","tid":319400,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T20:00:24.000Z","msg":"全撚部都呃鳩人"},{"pid":"abda9f968011c984ee4e1bbc36d13871752de3ad","tid":319400,"uid":16756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T20:04:54.000Z","msg":"1921 年 共產國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb1aea5584d29bacb30ebcf5ddd88b615b1b2c4","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T23:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教不來。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為中國歷史的教科書有許多矛盾和謊</span></span>言，其中一些，被中國的歷史學者自己踢爆，如「太平天國」之亂──國民黨的羅爾綱，共產黨的范文瀾和無數給「改造思想」的學者，都說是「革命」和「起義」，但近年許多大陸學者指出：什麼革命起義，不過是一個邪教。<br />\n<br />\n有些人睇咗電視劇或小說<br />\n就以為係真歷史<br />\n<br />\n宋朝就有人罵人係&quot;漢奸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岳飛破壞中華民族團結<br />\n<br />\n當時契丹(大遼國)比中原宋國強大<br />\n外國多跟契丹貿易<br />\n稱契丹為中國"},{"pid":"f375939daef576fd6ea41630a5a76ce79305b855","tid":319400,"uid":6964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T23:41:01.000Z","msg":"歷史係勝利嘅人寫"},{"pid":"2a8a91a3f2b1fa960a0c37e9aab138fc5f439013","tid":319400,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教不來。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為中國歷史的教科書有許多矛盾和謊</span></span>言，其中一些，被中國的歷史學者自己踢爆，如「太平天國」之亂──國民黨的羅爾綱，共產黨的范文瀾和無數給「改造思想」的學者，都說是「革命」和「起義」，但近年許多大陸學者指出：什麼革命起義，不過是一個邪教。<br />\n<br />\n有些人睇咗電視劇或小說<br />\n就以為係真歷史<br />\n<br />\n宋朝就有人罵人係&quot;漢奸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那拍建元風雲當正自己係蒙古人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe01496267fab48f3db2d3a69fe5eff96073418","tid":319400,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:10:47.000Z","msg":"近代中共歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n死幾多人"},{"pid":"6097f094e4e1c0527a17ccd98de99f59830aa9b2","tid":319400,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歷史係勝利嘅人寫</blockquote><br />\n可惜支那係失敗者<br />\n世界上唔係得支那狗架<br />\n你估冇其他人紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961223b1d0a834afcf2c71bf9a53dff6eef0bef3","tid":319400,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歷史係勝利嘅人寫</blockquote><br />\n可惜支那係失敗者<br />\n世界上唔係得支那狗架<br />\n你估冇其他人紀錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你， 你屌到咁應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後班支那狗點駁"},{"pid":"99da00006b80404e5d00e3112b2353355d072901","tid":319400,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:51:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a83f942b5bd3170463a8ac08bb71eb056fd35a24","tid":319400,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"其實咩叫 不平等條約 ？"},{"pid":"3292f3ae0d8ee74373d5cd561d98113eb9ef162a","tid":319400,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"越來越覺書本既中國歷史好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daae3b4b59b03c0cb18a34171afdd965b6daefc1","tid":319400,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實咩叫 不平等條約 ？</blockquote><br />\n我估同果D微電影呀 負資產呀 差唔多原理"},{"pid":"75a5283be097858d1a7ffb2c157139bc269feb45","tid":319400,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歷史從來是勝者為王，那有客觀的。就如聖誕節根本不是耶穌生日只時當時為了方便宣傳宗教而用當時的節日做借口以便宣傳。</blockquote><br />\nUp少陣廢話啦<br />\n如果支那係勝利者<br />\n點解呢個歷史真相仲有人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60b4017b8a3fb3ab1d37cb0cff9486a4e5fc6cf","tid":319400,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越來越覺書本既中國歷史好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係點維持大一統<br />\n<br />\n所以春秋戰國史官最盡責"},{"pid":"c30ef1dcaf73384cec6955afba3a8018cae4c625","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>越來越覺書本既中國歷史好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係點維持大一統<br />\n<br />\n所以春秋戰國史官最盡責</blockquote><br />\n春秋戰國只係中原一部份地方<br />\n正名&quot;中原歷史&quot;"},{"pid":"246c5e3880cd818bfbcb4043c8620094fd33777b","tid":319400,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"中共最叻篡改歷史"},{"pid":"fe365382a7ad33dc51bed5e12b3cc42c4dbe86e9","tid":319400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中共最叻篡改歷史</blockquote><br />\n國民黨咪係一樣"}]}